{"tid":1927863,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"武漢肺炎》移動生化武器？美國華人大媽挨家挨戶抹口水","createTime":"2020-03-16T04:59:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T05:15:54.000Z","uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0608c09b6c875d9b59f6d4c32f6f60b324243d95","tid":1927863,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T04:59:48.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎》移動生化武器？美國華人大媽挨家挨戶抹口水<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3100894\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3100894&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvpriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=49543ea5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3100894&h=90053dba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3100894</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國武漢肺炎已在美國造成數千例確診，當地民眾聞之色變，此時竟有加州華人大媽被發現在雨天出現在鄰居家門口，把自己的口水挨家挨戶地抹在鄰居家門把上，動機不明，恐怖行徑讓當地民眾膽顫心驚，台灣網友則驚呼：「移動式生化武器？」<br />\n<br />\n美國加州1名當事網友在個人臉書公布的2張照片與貼文，被轉傳至台灣批踢踢實業坊（PTT），照片內容是指稱1名華人大媽的「作案」過程，他敘述：「這個女人走上門來，舔了她的手指再碰門把，接著跑去其他鄰居們家幹同樣的事」。<br />\n<br />\n當事網友認為，婦人恐有散播病毒的嫌疑，公布她出現的地點位於美國加州的「Bellflower &amp; Arbor」，呼籲其他人若同樣發現這位大媽的行徑，請盡速聯絡萊克伍德（lakewood）警察局或長灘警察局（LBPD）。<br />\n<br />\n經查，嘗試在臉書搜尋該名當事網友的個人帳號，但對方的臉書隱私設定可能不允許被陌生用戶搜尋到，因此無法順利找出該名當事網友。<br />\n<br />\n不少台灣網友獲悉這起事件，質疑這位大媽是否從中國來的，稱呼她是「支那研發的新型武器」、「如果那傢伙是確診病患，那已經不是單純白目了，應該是標準的生化攻擊」、「這可能會引起美國大排華」、「她不怕被開槍嗎？」、「散播專員。病毒絕對是發源歐美」。"},{"pid":"8e78778e58b48d7af5f20a4baa6babafe1d4aad8","tid":1927863,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T05:01:11.000Z","msg":"排華<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b9be6c429d210436bbb9a4ab393b13ec5abfd16","tid":1927863,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T05:05:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">HERD IMMUNITY！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"dd7530b4c1c5eacc4e258744cd034cdf20cf8858","tid":1927863,"uid":168169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T05:06:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://twitter.com/v0gy0cic5bzonwl/status/1239189294700363777?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fv0gy0cic5bzonwl%2Fstatus%2F1239189294700363777%3Fs%3D21&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvpriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=47cdd8a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fv0gy0cic5bzonwl%2Fstatus%2F1239189294700363777%3Fs%3D21&h=19bc6c1c\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/v0gy0cic5bzonwl/status/1239189294700363777?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n［突發］有人整左維尼病毒公仔出嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1926864\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1926864</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"43db01c8a877827daf441cfa5c0846e94a5472d9","tid":1927863,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T05:08:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"350cbc4c6b9c83d5d1e80065c23311e4236d5916","tid":1927863,"uid":301820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T05:09:20.000Z","msg":"中国軍人嚟"},{"pid":"3a6deda0e5281a6c1868e8b892ce5d02a9d92e9b","tid":1927863,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T05:13:38.000Z","msg":"唔係話沒有起源咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2020/03/%E4%BD%95%E5%A4%A7%E4%B8%80-20200305115226_52cf_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2020%2F03%2F%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25B8%2580-20200305115226_52cf_large.jpg&h=afe5e8a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6aab69df3eeda5aa22333fe2f